text: "Now I'm Here" is a 1975 song by Queen and was taken from their studio album Sheer Heart Attack. It went to number 11 in the United Kingdom, number 29 in the Netherlands and Belgium and number 25 in Germany. It was covered by Def Leppard in 1992. == References == Category:1975 songs Category:Queen (band) songs Category:Def Leppard songs Category:Hard rock songs
title: Now I'm Here
